| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1339 — Recovery Inhibition (funksec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 55f74617-0a67-502b-b5e8-fb82dd9609fb"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
